{"type":"message","id":"1bdf3c8a","parentId":"80b2a7ad","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:27:29.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"With the Bearer token in the Authorization header, the key works and returns a lot of tools! The issue was that the key needs to be passed as a Bearer token in the Authorization header, not as a query parameter.\n\nLet me update the mcporter config to use the correct format with Authorization header, or inform the user.\n\nThe key `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` works with Bearer auth.\n\nThe existing config uses `?key=*** query param which didn't work. I need to update the mcporter config to use headers instead. But mcporter might not support custom headers easily. \n\nI should let the user know the key is valid and the server responds correctly when using Authorization Bearer header, but the current mcporter setup may need adjustment to pass the key as a header instead of a query parameter.\n","thinkingSignature":"0a66642b5e8a2c850fa6ba7ae0e03aa753c2fc1f6c69075c5df4009803332b6d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！问题是 auth 方式——要用 **Authorization: Bearer** header，而不是 query param。\n\n用 Bearer token 方式测试，key 完全正常，返回超多工具：\n\n```\nget_time → \"2026-03-06 10:23:01\"\n+ 几十个亚马逊/TikTok/Walmart 数据查询工具\n```\n\n**当前 mcporter 配置**（`?key=*** sorftime MCP 期望的是：\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer rhblyi…qt09\n```\n\n**剩余次数**：key 本身能正常调用，应该还有 92 次。你要我更新 mcporter 配置改成 Bearer header 方式吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":297,"output":322,"cacheRead":31680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32299,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778848032807,"responseId":"0656442101bfa1b67dddc710cac030c7"}}
