{"type":"message","id":"9cb46f27","parentId":"c3892285","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:35:25.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` works with Bearer auth and returns 56 tools. But `zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09` (the old configured key) still returns NotAuthorization with Bearer auth. \n\nThe old key `zwpmsm...zz09` works only when passed as `?key=*** query param but NOT when passed as Bearer header. And the new key `rhblyi...qt09` works with Bearer header.\n\nWait, but earlier when I tested `?key=sutbzf…t09` with query param it also returned NotAuthorization. \n\nActually, looking back at the first key the user mentioned (`sutbzfpknxhnaxrnzlczdddonutyut09`) - that also failed with query param. But `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` only works with Bearer header, not query param. So it seems like different keys might require different auth methods.\n\nThe real issue is that mcporter isn't sending the Authorization header to sorftime-mcp even though it's configured. Let me verify the header is actually being included in the request. Maybe the issue is with the URL format - the baseUrl is just `https://mcp.sorftime.com/` with the path stripped out, but the original URL had `/` on the end. mcporter only supports Bearer auth through headers but not query params, so the old key needs to be converted. I'll show the user that the new key works but confirm whether they want to use `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` as the primary key going forward.\n","thinkingSignature":"1b1fff5b3e3cce2a6f8ac6465f6f72c8f44131ea8961e7a6e351dc52b6f7ecc5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n发现问题了——`zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09` 这个旧的 key 只支持 query param 方式，而新 key `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` 必须用 Bearer header 方式。\n\n用 curl 直接测 Bearer header，新的 key 正常返回 **56 个工具**。\n\n但 mcporter 似乎没把 headers 里的 Authorization 传给服务——sorftime-mcp 依然返回 NotAuthorization。我来看看 mcporter 是否正确发送 headers：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7z7yog3nihkp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter list sorftime-test --schema 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":359,"output":530,"cacheRead":34752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35641,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778848505548,"responseId":"065645f97a8181248fcd283ea83b541d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"afe76792","parentId":"9cb46f27","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:35:28.569Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7z7yog3nihkp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"sorftime-test\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok电商平台**指定类目**的类目数据报告\n   *\n   * @param nodeId 类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_category_report(nodeId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": ["}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2572,"aggregated":"sorftime-test\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok电商平台**指定类目**的类目数据报告\n   *\n   * @param nodeId 类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_category_report(nodeId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778848528569}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d6b4f48","parentId":"afe76792","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:35:43.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so:\n- `sorftime-test` (with key `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`) works with Bearer header via mcporter and returns 56 tools\n- `sorftime-mcp` (with key `zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09`) does NOT work - returns NotAuthorization\n\nSo the `zwpmsm...` key might be invalid, revoked, or expired. The `rhblyi...` key works fine.\n\nThe user said they paid for 30092 times. Maybe the `rhblyi...` key is the paid one and has 30092 uses remaining. Let me inform the user about this.\n","thinkingSignature":"6d97b67bb279dc2bbda0887d5fa8725bf46d77cf427f2bc8020b0559ba6bee38"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` 这个 key 可以正常工作 ✅，通过 mcporter 能调用到 56 个工具（亚马逊、TikTok、Walmart 数据查询）。\n\n但 `zwpmsmvutwvimcs2mmlzu2vyl3dkzz09` 这个 key 返回 `NotAuthorization`，说明这个 key 有问题。\n\n你可以确认一下：\n1. 30092 次是哪个 key？\n2. `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` 是不是你刚付费生成的那个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":329,"output":285,"cacheRead":35008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35622,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778848528615,"responseId":"065646126faf66acb977123f1985d43d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1676ae05","parentId":"5d6b4f48","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:35:50.583Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f45626170acb291d2088004320]\nou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 选品策略2.0 26.5.14\n\n你是专属越南TikTok Shop时尚配件\\-发饰类目选品Agent，拥有Sorftime全套MCP权限：亚马逊MCP、TikTok Shop全套MCP、1688 MCP；已对接飞书多维表格，\\*\\*严格使用我提供的固定成本&利润计算公式核算\\*\\*，禁止自定义估算，目标站点：越南站，精准类目：时尚配件\\-发饰\\-发箍、发夹、发簪。\n\n\\#\\# 一、成本核算强制规则\n1. 所有产品的净利润、平台扣点、物流费、广告预留、到手利润，\\*\\*100%套用我提供的成本计算公式\\*\\*，不允许自行调整参数。\n2. 仅保留【核算后真实净利润≥35%】的产品，不达标直接剔除。\n\n\\#\\# 二、MCP调用固定顺序（必须严格执行，不可跳过）\n1. 第一步：调用亚马逊similar\\_product\\_feature\n关键词：hair clips、hair hoops、hairpins，查询美区/东南亚热销发饰共性爆款特征（款式、材质、颜色、风格、尺寸、卖点），锁定越南市场适配的爆款基因，排除欧美小众风格。\n2. 第二步：调用TikTok Shop越南站全套MCP\n基于亚马逊爆款特征，筛选候选品池，硬性条件：\n \\- 上架＜3个月新品\n \\- 近4周销量持续上涨，无下滑\n \\- 中小达人（1w–5w粉）带货为主，无头部卖家垄断\n \\- 商品评分≥4.5，差评少、无侵权风险\n \\- 价格带适配越南站，避开超低价内卷\n3. 第三步：调用1688 ali1688\\_similar\\_product\n对TikTok候选品逐个查询：拿货价、供应商、起订量、货源稳定性，套用成本公式核算真实利润，剔除利润不足、货源不稳的款。\n\n\\#\\# 三、交叉对比评分权重（总分100，横向排序）\n1. 公式核算后真实利润：35分\n2. TikTok越南站销量增长趋势：25分\n3. 竞争友好度（中小达人占比、头部垄断情况）：20分\n4. 亚马逊同款海外成熟热销度：12分\n5. 越南本地审美适配\\+短视频易拍摄种草：8分\n\n\\#\\# 四、强制剔除红线\n1. 风格不符合越南年轻女性审美（欧美夸张、暗黑风、宗教敏感款）\n2. 低价内卷品、销量衰退品、易碎易断品、侵权款、起订量过高款\n3. 利润核算后低于35%的全部淘汰\n\n\\#\\# 五、飞书多维表格入库核心规则\n1. \\*\\*仅入库最终筛选的Top3–Top10高潜爆款，海量原始候选品、中间对比品不入库，保持表格简洁\\*\\*\n2. 入库固定字段：产品标题、TikTok越南站售价、1688拿货价、公式计算真实净利润、近4周销量趋势、竞争等级、风险提示、上架定价&投流建议、核心卖点\n3. 入库完成后，同步在对话内输出精简版选品结果\n\n现在直接启动全流程选品，输出越南站发箍/发夹/发簪高潜爆款。"}],"timestamp":1778848550581}}
