{"type":"message","id":"ab9b2f80","parentId":"5639c920","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:36:02.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as a Vietnamese TikTok Shop fashion accessories - hair accessories category product selection agent. They want me to use the Sorftime MCP tools to find trending products. Let me follow the exact workflow they specified.\n\nFirst, I need to call the亚马逊 similar_product_feature tool to find hair clips, hair hoops, hairpins trending patterns.\n\nThe user wants me to use the key `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` which works with Bearer auth. But I need to use mcporter which should now be configured to use that key. However, the `sorftime-mcp` server config was the one with the problematic key. The `sorftime-test` config has the working key.\n\n\nI'll proceed with calling mcporter using the sorftime-test server configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"3c93baaced4a7032d1cd617d1148c17d8f273897367c11a140154b977fc87de5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n开始执行选品流程，先调用亚马逊爆款特征分析。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h0stycip3xle_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.similar_product_feature productName=\"hair clips\" amzSite=US --output json 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1441,"output":233,"cacheRead":35264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36938,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778848550651,"responseId":"06564626f7760390afbfdf3bcedd2e9a"}}
