{"type":"message","id":"a7691d8d","parentId":"bf22943a","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:42:48.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also check the product detail and trend for the top candidates from TikTok Vietnam to understand their pricing and sales trends. Then I can cross-reference with 1688 costs.\n\nFrom TikTok Vietnam data, the top candidates are:\n1. Set 6 Dây Buộc Tóc Lò Xo (elastic hair ties) - 16999 VND, 30285 monthly sales\n2. Kẹp Chuối (Banana clip) - 17000 VND, 10768 monthly sales\n3. Kẹp Tóc Càng Cua (Claw clip) - various prices around 16000-19999 VND\n4. Băng Đô (Headband) - 34780 VND for the French floral one\n\n\n5. Bờm Tạo Phồng (Hair bump/puff) - 20999 VND, 7791 monthly sales\n\nI'm noticing that Băng Đô Pháp floral headband stands out as one of the few items with positive growth at +0.61% week-over-week, while most other products are declining. I should verify whether this item qualifies as newly listed and examine its sales momentum more closely.\n\nNow I need to check which tools are actually available for the product details and categories.\n","thinkingSignature":"a8fcc9ef9f25629be2ef073bfe69234ce9af514585f7209204c33ff1a92e938a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1xjtt28zmcv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.category_name_search categoryName=\"hair accessories\" amzSite=US --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1xjtt28zmcv_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.tiktok_similar_product searchName=\"bông cài tóc\" page=1 site=VN --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3058,"output":399,"cacheRead":58944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62401,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778848950797,"responseId":"065647b74d157940c7125b0d15778901"}}
