{"type":"message","id":"c81fc9ea","parentId":"42418f07","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:43:18.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the category report for the claw clip category and also check a few more 1688 products to get actual supply prices for the candidate products.\n\nBased on the TikTok data I've gathered, the top candidates for Vietnam TikTok Shop in hair accessories are:\n1. **Kẹp Càng Cua / Claw clips** - tons of products, various styles\n2. **Kẹp Nơ / Bow clips** - butterfly, ribbon, bow styles\n3. **Băng Đô / Headbands** - but mostly sports/anti-slip types\n4. **Dây buộc tóc / Hair ties** - large pack quantities\n\n\n5. **Miếng dán tóc / Hair stickers** - cat ears, facial hair stickers\n\nThe Vietnamese market clearly favors Korean-inspired styles, large pieces with ribbon and bow details, cute animal designs, soft and pastel color palettes, and bulk packaging. I'm also seeing a strong emphasis on new product launches from sellers like Phụ Kiện Alia, Vua Kẹp Tóc, and M.A.I COSMETICS, so I should dig deeper into their specific offerings.\n","thinkingSignature":"63c296964917eeb10a79751ab167ac2bef049f9c5f857f7d875c96cd69aa2d95"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pj2rfk0cs1ce_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"crisp-basil","timeout":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pj2rfk0cs1ce_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.category_report nodeId=23623510011 amzSite=US --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":20000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":410,"output":348,"cacheRead":61888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62646,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778848984150,"responseId":"065647d820f21dd426f050d4c095695f"}}
