{"type":"message","id":"24d46631","parentId":"649e49d7","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:46:06.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 1688 results are very repetitive - it's returning the same products regardless of search term. This might be a limitation of the MCP tool. Let me try different product-specific searches to get relevant 1688 pricing for the specific TikTok Vietnam products.\n\nLet me now take stock of what I have and start building the analysis. I need the user's cost calculation formula. Let me ask about it since it's critical.\n\nActually, let me think about this more carefully. The user said to use \"我提供的固定成本&利润计算公式\". But they haven't provided it in this conversation. I need to ask.\n\nLet me compile what I have so far and present a preliminary analysis, while asking for the cost formula.\n\n\nNow I'm looking at the key products I've identified from TikTok Vietnam: the Set 6 Dây Buộc Tóc Lò Xo coil hair ties at 16,999 VND with strong sales of 30,285 monthly, and the Bộ 136 Chiếc Dây Cột Tóc bulk pack at 44,999 VND with 23,470 monthly sales - both from M.A.I COSMETICS and Gia Dụng DTA-999.\n\nI'm also seeing several other strong performers: Kẹp Chuối banana clip at 17,000 VND with 10,768 sales from Phụ Kiện Alia, the Kẹp Tóc Càng Cua crab clip at 16,000 VND with 9,783 sales also from Phụ Kiện Alia, and the Băng Đô headband at 8,998 VND with 9,588 sales from Kim Nguyên Bến Tre.\n\nThere's also the Kẹp Tóc Nơ bouncy bow clip at 14,000 VND with 6,074 sales from Love Accessories Factory Store, and another bouncy bow variant at 19,499 VND with 6,058 monthly sales from the same seller.\n\nNow I'm cross-referencing these with Amazon's top performers in the hair claw category. The top products are selling between 13,000-21,800 units monthly at price points ranging from $7.99 to $9.99, with brands like Kitsch, LuSeren, and SMKSL dominating the market.\n\nI'm noticing the Vietnam market has different price points and stronger growth signals for new entrants, so I should focus on identifying which products there show the most promising upward momentum rather than just replicating the Amazon rankings.\n","thinkingSignature":"59a81dfffed6bbfb98d18f4378bd708d94db39c4219557e39bdeab7709f7a70d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m9bvkhvj5asf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.product_trend asin=B0DQDP625C productTrendType=SalesVolume amzSite=US --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m9bvkhvj5asf_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.product_trend asin=B09G3HHZ7F productTrendType=SalesVolume amzSite=US --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1234,"output":658,"cacheRead":73472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849132647,"responseId":"0656486d26ac8c474f11ae1a019a7440"}}
