{"type":"message","id":"34a2df54","parentId":"12ce1624","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:48:17.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to read the feishu skill to understand how to integrate with their Feishu spreadsheet. The user mentioned \"飞书多维表格\" - Feishu bidirectional tables (like Airtable).\n","thinkingSignature":"85bfa305b0850aea5dcb0b80fd0010ec0833ee43d06966ce7eb1af9bc31771ed"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aqjg5s5nx976_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":278,"output":83,"cacheRead":76608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849286960,"responseId":"06564907415dc777aa3aed331f976b8f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"076d928b","parentId":"34a2df54","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:48:17.787Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aqjg5s5nx976_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations, including table creation for Docx.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\nReplaces entire document with markdown content. Supports: headings, lists, code blocks, quotes, links, images (`![](url)` auto-uploaded), bold/italic/strikethrough.\n\n**Limitation:** Markdown tables are NOT supported.\n\n### Append Content\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"append\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"Additional content\" }\n```\n\nAppends markdown to end of document.\n\n### Create Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"title\": \"New Document\", \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\" }\n```\n\nWith folder:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"title\": \"New Document\",\n  \"folder_token\": \"fldcnXXX\",\n  \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n**Important:** Always pass `owner_open_id` with the requesting user's `open_id` (from inbound metadata `sender_id`) so the user automatically gets `full_access` permission on the created document. Without this, only the bot app has access.\n\n### List Blocks\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"list_blocks\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns full block data including tables, images. Use this to read structured content.\n\n### Get Single Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"get_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Update Block Text\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update_block\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\",\n  \"content\": \"New text\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"delete_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Create Table (Docx Table Block)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Write Table Cells\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"write_table_cells\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"table_block_id\": \"doxcnTABLE\",\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Create Table With Values (One-step)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table_with_values\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200],\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Upload Image to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/image.png\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path with position control:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/image.png\",\n  \"parent_block_id\": \"doxcnParent\",\n  \"index\": 5\n}\n```\n\nOptional `index` (0-based) inserts the image at a specific position among sibling blocks. Omit to append at end.\n\n**Note:** Image display size is determined by the uploaded image's pixel dimensions. For small images (e.g. 480x270 GIFs), scale to 800px+ width before uploading to ensure proper display.\n\n### Upload File Attachment to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/report.pdf\",\n  \"filename\": \"Q1-report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nRules:\n\n- exactly one of `url` / `file_path`\n- optional `filename` override\n- optional `parent_block_id`\n\n## Reading Workflow\n\n1. Start with `action: \"read\"` - get plain text + statistics\n2. Check `block_types` in response for Table, Image, Code, etc.\n3. If structured content exists, use `action: \"list_blocks\"` for full data\n\n## Configuration\n\n```yaml\nchannels:\n  feishu:\n    tools:\n      doc: true # default: true\n```\n\n**Note:** `feishu_wiki` depends on this tool - wiki page content is read/written via `feishu_doc`.\n\n## Permissions\n\nRequired: `docx:document`, `docx:document:readonly`, `docx:document.block:convert`, `drive:drive`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778849297787}}
{"type":"message","id":"47e602e1","parentId":"076d928b","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:48:52.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the feishu-doc skill. I need to know the doc token for the user's Feishu spreadsheet. But the user hasn't provided a specific doc link. Let me ask about it. \n\nActually, looking at the user's prompt again, they mention \"已对接飞书多维表格\" - they've already connected to a Feishu spreadsheet. But they haven't provided the doc link/token. I should ask for it.\n\nWait - actually, let me re-read. The user said \"你是专属越南TikTok Shop时尚配件\\-发饰类目选品Agent...已对接飞书多维表格\" - this suggests they've already set up the connection. But I don't have the doc token. I should ask for it.\n\n\nI realize I don't have the specific doc link or token they mentioned connecting to, so I need to request that information to proceed.\n","thinkingSignature":"e67e1c83fe6097a6d218d79458e093457f842d98ed999c386093324ca8e6eab6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n数据收集完毕，但我需要你提供飞书多维表格的链接才能入库。请把你的飞书表格链接发给我（格式如 `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/xxx`）。\n\n同时先给你整理一下目前的选品分析结果：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 亚马逊爆款基因分析（美区 Hair Claws 类目）\n\n**月销量趋势：** 2026年5月 ~30.6万 / 月，旺季（12月）峰值 57.7万，整体持续增长\n\n**核心爆款特征（高销量占比）：**\n- 🦴 **Claw Clips（大号爪夹）** — 销量最大，均价$7-10\n- 防滑+牢固+多尺寸套装是核心卖点\n- 哑光/磨砂材质 > 光泽材质\n- Kitsch、Sisiaipu、SMKSL 三个品牌垄断 top\n\n**越南适配爆款基因：**\n- 韩系/日系审美（粉色、奶油色、玳瑁色）\n- 小号/中号多件套（3-12pcs）更易起量\n- 蝴蝶结/猫耳/花朵等可爱元素\n- 价格带 $8-25K VND（低客单价友好）\n\n---\n\n## 🇻🇳 TikTok 越南站 Top 候选（已筛选）\n\n### 🔥 高潜爆款候选（按综合评分排序）\n\n| 排名 | 产品 | 越南售价 | 周销量趋势 | 星级 | 风险 |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | Kẹp tóc nơ lụa bản to（丝带大蝴蝶结） | 39,000₫ | +20%+ | ⭐4.9 | ⚠️竞争激烈 |\n| 2 | Kẹp xược độn phồng tóc（蓬松发片夹） | 22,500₫ | +22.9% ↑ | ⭐4.5 | ✅竞争友好 |\n| 3 | Kẹp Tóc Càng Cua Nơ Cỡ Lớn（蝴蝶结爪夹） | 48,800₫ | 持平 | ⭐4.7 | ⚠️头部垄断 |\n| 4 | Kẹp tóc nơ bông（丝绒蝴蝶结发夹） | 35,000₫ | 持平 | ⭐4.8 | ✅ |\n| 5 | Băng đô dán dính floral（花朵发带） | 34,780₫ | +0.6% | ⭐4.7 | ✅竞争小 |\n| 6 | Miếng dán tóc mái（刘海贴片） | 14,999₫ | +5% | ⭐4.8 | ✅新形态 |\n\n---\n\n## 💰 1688 供应链价格（关键候选）\n\n| 产品类型 | 1688拿货价 | 越南售价 | 毛利率估算 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 丝带大蝴蝶结爪夹 | ¥1.5-3.8 | 39,000₫ | ~65-72% |\n| 蓬松发片夹 | ¥2-4 | 22,500₫ | ~55-62% |\n| 丝绒蝴蝶结 | ¥1-2 | 35,000₫ | ~70-78% |\n| 花朵发带 | ¥1.6-2.5 | 34,780₫ | ~68-75% |\n| 刘海贴片套装 | ¥0.3-1 | 14,999₫ | ~75-82% |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 需要你提供的信息\n\n**请给我飞书多维表格链接**，我直接把 Top6 爆款的结构化数据写入表格。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1412,"output":980,"cacheRead":76800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778849297907,"responseId":"065649129adc6625ac61cc95502f30e3"}}
