88拿货价区间 |\n|---|---|\n| 丝带大蝴蝶结 | ¥1.5-3.8 |\n| 蓬松发片夹 | ¥2-4 |\n| 花朵发带 | ¥1.6-2.5 |\n| 刘海贴片套装 | ¥0.3-1 |\n| 丝绒蝴蝶结 | ¥1-2 |\n\n---\n\n**等你发成本公式，我马上跑利润核算 + 交叉评分 + 入库飞书。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12086,"output":872,"cacheRead":73216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86174,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778850086945,"responseId":"06564c27d5008d5d373178f0c89bb201"}}
