ing out.\n","thinkingSignature":"b8d36bf5498b2890051cd5589e28606cf8fa65ebce49d45530615fda2975223d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n图片 OCR 识别环境还没配好（缺 tesseract 权限）。麻烦你把成本公式截图里的**文字内容直接复制粘贴发给我**，或者手动把公式字段列出来：\n\n需要的关键参数：\n1. **售价 / Sale Price**\n2. **拿货价 / 货本**\n3. **平台佣金比例**（%）\n4. **国际运费**\n5. **广告预留比例**（%）\n6. **其他费用（如有）**\n\n发给我之后我立刻跑完整核算 + 飞书入库。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":263,"output":528,"cacheRead":87744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778850631577,"responseId":"06564e48226d15868eb28afa55b227ff"}}
