{"type":"message","id":"2c9853b2","parentId":"4ba51f67","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:26:15.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying these products' prices are too low (on the Vietnam TikTok Shop). They want products that are 60,000 VND or above. Let me go back to the TikTok Vietnam data and find higher-priced items (≥60,000 VND).\n\nFrom the category report data I already collected, let me look for items with price ≥ 60,000 VND:\n\nFrom the tiktok_category_report nodeId=908552 (Hair Clips & Hair Pins):\n- Set 50 Kẹp Tóc Dễ Thương... - 86,300₫ (set of 50, but this is a bulk set)\n- COMBO 5 KẸP 5 MÀU - 69,999₫\n\n\n- Kẹp Tóc Lì Đơn Giản... - 37,536₫ (too low)\n\nLooking at tiktok_similar_product results for \"Kẹp tóc nơ\", I'm seeing several mid-range options like the 30,285-unit set at 16,999₫ and a 23,470-unit set at 44,999₫, though both fall short of the 60,000 threshold.\n\nScanning higher-priced items in the category report, I find the large silk bow clip at 48,800₫ which qualifies, along with a 49,000₫ option, but most other products in this range are bulk or children's sets rather than individual units. The data is quite limited for items priced at 60,000₫ or above. I'm looking at more product listings with their ratings and review counts to assess popularity and quality. The pricing seems mixed—some items are in the lower range around 9,000-17,000 VND, while others jump significantly higher like the 46,000-49,000 VND range. I notice several products have strong ratings of 4.7 or 4.8 stars with thousands of reviews, which suggests these are more established sellers rather than new entrants. Looking at the product data, most items are priced between 16,000-49,000₫, with only a few reaching 60,000₫ or higher like the 86,300₫ set. I'm also checking the product_similar results for \"hair clip claw\" to see what Vietnamese products are actually available in that category. Looking at the data more carefully, products priced at 60,000 VND or higher appear to be either bulk/combo sets or premium/specialty items. Let me pull a fresh search to find more mid-to-high price range products in that category.\n","thinkingSignature":"ead4f994348ca11fc8483d4a05c2440ba4ce870796de753decd63972b138d282"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，找价格 60,000₫ 以上的款！我重新筛选一下越南TikTok上的高价候选品。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fixk72kr84cs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.tiktok_category_report nodeId=908552 site=VN --output json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('=== 月销38万，全部价格带分布 ===')\nproducts = data.get('Top50产品', [])\nhigh_price = [p for p in products if p.get('价格', 0) >= 60000]\nprint(f'60K以上产品共 {len(high_price)} 个:')\nfor p in sorted(high_price, key=lambda x: -x.get('月销量', 0)):\n    print(f\\\"  {p['价格']:>8}₫ | 周环比{p['周销量环比']:>+6.1f}% | 月销{p['月销量']:>5} | ★{p['星级']} | {p['标题'][:50]}\\\")\n\" 2>&1","yieldMs":20000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fixk72kr84cs_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.tiktok_similar_product searchName=\"kẹp tóc cao cấp\" page=1 site=VN --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fixk72kr84cs_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.tiktok_similar_product searchName=\"hair clip set\" page=1 site=VN --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38123,"output":934,"cacheRead":51712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90769,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778851535614,"responseId":"065651d1f8edac1df1bef0119a973053"}}
