positive/neutral growth\ncandidates = [\n    (\"Scrunchies\", 908424, \"Lò xo cột tóc thailann phồng tóc\", 59000, 4888, -14.29, 4.5, \"Thiên Nhiên Ý\"),\n    (\"Scrunchies\", 908424, \"Túi 500 sợi chun bông xù cột tóc cho bé\", 48999, 4373, -3.77, 4.7, \"Phụ Kiện thơ Bùi Hảo\"),\n    (\"Scrunchies\", 908424, \"Sét 10 Chun Thái Lò Xo (上升趋势!)\", 49000, 2978, 20.75, 4.6, \"Gia Bảo Shop 103\"),\n    (\"Scrunchies\", 908424, \"Cột tóc ren 4 lớp cỡ lớn dày cho nữ #700\", 35000, 1430, -14.29, 4.7, \"Kẹp tóc Nhà Mây\"),\n    (\"Scrunchies\", 908424, \"Sét chun buộc tóc 136 chi tiết siêu co giãn\", 39997, 1115, -14.4, 4.7, \"Gia Dụng MiMi\"),\n    (\"Scrunchies\", 908424, \"LAM MISA Băng Đô Tóc Nữ Cao Cấp chống trượt\", 38000, 1115, -17.56, 4.7, \"Lam misa Việt Nam\"),\n    (\"Baby发饰\", 962696, \"Set 50 kẹp tóc dễ thương màu hồng cho bé gái (暴涨!)\", 36000, 13428, 88.47, 4.1, \"Kho Hàng Gia Dụng 4 Mùa\"),\n    (\"Baby发饰\", 962696, \"Túi 50 Dây Buộc Tóc Cho Bé Siêu xịn túi zip tim\", 38700, 2566, -3.83, 4.7, \"Đồ dùng tiện ích 86-88\"),\n    (\"Baby发饰\", 962696, \"Hộp quà 156 chi tiết phụ kiện cho bé kèm túi đựng\", 159999, 789, -14.29, 3.9, \"Tiểu Mụi Mụi Phụ kiện\"),\n    (\"Baby发饰\", 962696, \"Vương miện vải đội đầu sinh nhật đầy tháng cho bé (暴涨!)\", 48400, 521, 29.67, 4.9, \"MiniMom- Thêu Tên Cho Bé\"),\n    (\"Baby发饰\", 962696, \"Sét 10 miếng dán tóc tạo kiểu cho bé\", 59000, 1619, -38.43, 4.7, \"Tiểu Mụi Mụi Phụ kiện\"),\n    (\"Baby发饰\", 962696, \"Set 32 Kẹp Tách Nhiều Màu Xinh Xắn Cho Bé\", 32500, 2236, -1.83, 4.7, \"Tổng kho Sỉ gia dụng Anh Tú\"),\n    (\"发夹\", 908552, \"[COMBO 5] Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá (高价爆款!)\", 69999, 5333, -14.29, 4.6, \"SÂU HOUSE\"),\n    (\"发夹\", 908552, \"Set 50 Kẹp Tóc Dễ Thương NOVSET cho bé gái\", 86300, 3221, -29.21, 4.2, \"NovsetHN\"),\n]\n\n# Filter for ≥60K and positive/good trend\nprint(\"【≥60K + 增长/稳定】\")\nprint()\nhigh_candidates = [\n    c for c in candidates \n    if c[3] >= 60000 and c[5] > -20\n]\nfor cat, node, title, price, mo, growth, star, seller in sorted(high_candidates, key=lambda x: -x[4]):\n    trend_icon = \"📈\" if growth > 10 else \"📉\" if growth < -10 else \"➡️\"\n    print(f\"  {trend_icon} {price:>7,}₫ | 周{growth:>+5.1f}% | 月销{mo:,} | ★{star} | {seller}\")\n    print(f\"     {title[:60]}\")\n    print()\nEOF\npython3 /dev/stdin << 'EOF'\nprint(\"=== 60K+ 高价增长候选品 ===\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13922,"output":3179,"cacheRead":94848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111949,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778851676468,"responseId":"0656525dcfb177b622375cea17fa0d75"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4399c27","parentId":"d9b19555","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:29:38.706Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4i7z5p1h85xn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 越南TikTok >60K VND 高价候选品（已排除下滑款）===\n\n【≥60K + 增长/稳定】\n\n  📉  69,999₫ | 周-14.3% | 月销5,333 | ★4.6 | SÂU HOUSE\n     [COMBO 5] Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá (高价爆款!)\n\n  📉 159,999₫ | 周-14.3% | 月销789 | ★3.9 | Tiểu Mụi Mụi Phụ kiện\n     Hộp quà 156 chi tiết phụ kiện cho bé kèm túi đựng\n\n=== 60K+ 高价增长候选品 ==="}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":57,"aggregated":"=== 越南TikTok >60K VND 高价候选品（已排除下滑款）===\n\n【≥60K + 增长/稳定】\n\n  📉  69,999₫ | 周-14.3% | 月销5,333 | ★4.6 | SÂU HOUSE\n     [COMBO 5] Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá (高价爆款!)\n\n  📉 159,999₫ | 周-14.3% | 月销789 | ★3.9 | Tiểu Mụi Mụi Phụ kiện\n     Hộp quà 156 chi tiết phụ kiện cho bé kèm túi đựng\n\n=== 60K+ 高价增长候选品 ===","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778851778706}}
{"type":"message","id":"32938ae6","parentId":"b4399c27","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:30:17.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The analysis shows very few products above 60K VND with positive growth in the hair accessories category. The reality is:\n\n1. The Vietnam TikTok hair accessories market is heavily dominated by LOW-PRICE products (majority < 40K VND)\n2. Products above 60K VND tend to be:\n   - Large combo/sets (50-500 pieces)\n   - Premium/bundled gift sets\n   - Baby accessories (which have higher unit prices)\n\nThe user is saying the product prices are too low and wants 60K+ products. But from the data, the high-value segment in this category is relatively thin.\n\nHowever, the user wants higher-priced products - which suggests they might want to either:\n\n\n1. Focus on the higher-priced segments (gift sets, large combos, premium items)\n2. Consider a different sub-category within fashion accessories\n3. Reconsider the price floor\n\nThe real opportunity in the 60K+ range appears to be in gift sets and premium bundles rather than single items - sets of 10-50 pieces that justify the higher price point through quantity.\n\nGiven the strategy emphasizes claw clips, hair clips, and hairpins with a 35% net profit floor, single pieces in this category are genuinely constrained to lower price bands. But I'm also noticing the Baby Hair Accessories category has some interesting dynamics worth exploring. The 60K+ segment in the regular hair accessories category is fairly sparse, but there are some solid performers in the baby accessories space—Set 50 hair clips for girls at 36K with strong 88% week-over-week growth and solid ratings, plus a crown headband item at 48,400 that could work as a gift set angle.\n\nFor higher price points, I'm thinking the user might be better off shifting toward premium gift sets, large-quantity combo packs, or cross-category expansion into fashion accessories like necklaces and earrings rather than staying narrowly focused on hair accessories. Alternatively, positioning hair accessories as complementary add-ons to higher-ticket fashion items could justify the 60K+ price range.\n\nI should be straightforward about the market reality here—the data doesn't naturally support that price point in this category alone, so I need to either reframe their expectations or propose a strategic pivot before we lock into specific SKUs and 1688 pricing.\n","thinkingSignature":"c791e4f51625628d813ccf98c7fd76285d74e3bf8d757ef2d316adc8e6ca5cb0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n说实话，数据很现实——\n\n---\n\n## 📊 真实市场情况\n\n越南 TikTok 发饰品类 **80%+ 销量集中在 10K-40K VND 低价带**，60K 以上的高价产品**数量少、增长慢**，且大多是：\n\n- 超大套装（50-500件捆绑）\n- 婴儿发饰（单价天然更高）\n- 礼品盒套装\n\n单件发夹/发箍/发簪要做到 60K+ VND 几乎都要走**套装或礼品路线**。\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 两个方向，你选哪个？\n\n### 方向 A：坚守 60K+ → 转型套装/礼品定位\n把发饰**重新包装成礼品套装**，例如：\n- \"12件套韩系发夹礼盒\" → 定价 89,000₫\n- \"20件套开学礼物套装\" → 定价 99,000₫\n- \"50件套发饰福袋\" → 定价 159,000₫\n\n这样拿货价虽然更高（¥5-15），但**件数多 → 性价比感知强 → 客单价冲上60K**\n\n### 方向 B：聚焦 35K-60K 主流价格带\n这个区间其实竞争最健康、达人生态最好。**35K-60K 才是越南发饰的黄金价格带**，真正跑量的爆款都集中在这里：\n- 25,000₫ 蓬松发片夹（我的 Top1 候选）\n- 35,000₫ 丝绒蝴蝶结\n- 38,000₫ 丝带大蝴蝶结\n- 48,800₫ 蝴蝶结爪夹大套装\n\n---\n\n**你怎么想？** 选 A 我重新按套装方向筛选 1688，拿货价和利润重新套公式算；选 B 我直接拿之前的候选品继续走成本核算 + 入库流程。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2896,"output":874,"cacheRead":108672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112442,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778851778816,"responseId":"065652c4c5693ed7cf03b3c47e067e3d"}}
