{"type":"message","id":"88e7da93","parentId":"6d4ca87b","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:35:22.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 1688 search results aren't showing combo/set products. The `ali1688_similar_product` function seems to search by product name/keyword and return individual products. I need to search for specific terms like \"套装\", \"组合\", \"礼盒\" in Chinese to find combo products.\n\nLet me try more specific searches for combo/set products with Vietnamese market in mind. The user showed me their product which is a combo of 3-4 items. Let me search for:\n1. \"发饰 套装 跨境 越南\" \n2. \"发夹 套装 礼盒 组合\"\n\n\n3. \"韩国发饰 套装 多件\" (Korean style hair accessories set)\n\nLooking at the prices the user provided, I'm noticing something odd - their combo product at 120-140K VND has a 1688 cost of 36.20 CNY, which converts to about 140,000 VND. That's essentially a 1:1 markup, which doesn't make sense for a wholesale product. Either they're selling their own manufactured product directly rather than dropshipping from 1688, or there's something else going on with the pricing structure.\n\nIf this is their own private label product manufactured in China, then asking me to find similar products on 1688 wouldn't help - they'd need to source the individual components instead. But the more practical question is probably whether the `ali1688_similar_product` function can handle combo products at all, since the search results seem to be returning individual items. I should try searching for Vietnamese keywords or more specific terms like \"3件套\" or \"4件套\" to see if I can find actual combo products on the platform.\n","thinkingSignature":"2b986d529085708a528ecdabbc1a5181cb81f4250244ae55ee15c953df71857f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8a1uvbaec8z5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call sorftime-test.ali1688_similar_product searchName=\"发饰 套装 三件套 四件套 礼盒\" page=1 --output json 2>&1","yieldMs":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id