{"type":"message","id":"6a28b1c2","parentId":"a4cd1b75","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:38:36.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 1688 MCP `ali1688_similar_product` tool seems to be returning very generic/popular results regardless of the search query. It keeps returning the same set of products - mostly single-piece items like sports headbands, basic hair clips, etc. It's not finding the \"套装\" (set/combo) products.\n\nThis might be a limitation of the MCP tool - it might just do a simple keyword match and return whatever is popular, rather than truly understanding the query. Or the search index might not have good set/combo products under those keywords.\n\nLet me try a different approach. I can try:\n1. Direct search terms that include Chinese characters for \"combo/set\" - which I've been trying\n\n\n2. Maybe I need to try more specific searches\n\nI should also ask what specific type of product they want (what's in the 4-combo they're selling?), and try broader terms. But actually, let me just be honest about the 1688 MCP limitation and suggest a workaround. The tool seems to be returning the same popular items regardless of search terms, which suggests either the tool has a limited index, returns pre-sorted results, or the search isn't working as expected. I'm noticing some products appear consistently - the ¥1.99 and ¥1.78 headbands, ¥4.6 and ¥3.1 items - which might indicate the search is pulling from a cached or non-randomized result set.\n\nThe core issue is that the 1688 search tool isn't surfacing combo/set products at all. Instead of continuing to bang my head against this, I should pivot to direct searching with simpler terms like \"套装\" or \"组合\", or I could try using Amazon data to identify top sellers and then source those specific products from 1688 directly. I'll be transparent about the limitation and suggest we work around it by building a combo ourselves from individual high-margin items we can find, rather than finding pre-packaged sets.\n","thinkingSignature":"940d5d3430a08c6d13176f66fbe2f66dfa171af11e9fc275acfcc34c1f42ebe7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n1688 的搜索结果一直返回的是爆款单品，不是套装。这个 MCP 工具搜套装不太准确。\n\n换个思路——我直接从亚马逊爆款里选**单件高利润单品**，然后**自己搭配成套装**。先来看几组可组套的候选：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 1688 可组套候选品（亚马逊爆款基因 + 越南市场适配）\n\n根据之前亚马逊 Hair Claws 类目爆款数据，以下单品拿货价低、利润空间大，**适合 3-4 件组套冲到 60K+ VND**：\n\n### 方案 A：丝带蝴蝶结套装（目标售价 119K₫）\n\n| 部件 | 1688拿货价 | 供应商 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 丝带大蝴蝶结发夹 | ¥1.5-2.5 | 义乌奕展日用品厂 |\n| 韩系粉色波点发夹 | ¥3.8 | 义乌极佳电子商务 |\n| 玳瑁色爪夹（中号） | ¥2-3 | 义乌慧娴饰品 |\n\n**套装拿货成本：¥7-9**，组3件→定价119K₫\n**毛利估算：~72-75%** ✅\n\n---\n\n### 方案 B：花系发饰礼盒套装（目标售价 139K₫）\n\n| 部件 | 1688拿货价 | 供应商 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 花朵发带（大号） | ¥2.5-3.5 | 义乌浩福饰品 |\n| 兔耳发箍（毛绒） | ¥1.88-2.5 | 义乌益选饰品 |\n| 蝴蝶结发圈 | ¥1.5-2 | 义乌妹妹饰品 |\n\n**套装拿货成本：¥6-8**，组3件→定价139K₫\n**毛利估算：~68-74%** ✅\n\n---\n\n### 方案 C：高颅顶发箍套装（目标售价 99K₫）\n\n| 部件 | 1688拿货价 | 供应商 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 闪钻王妃发箍 | ¥1.5 | 义乌奕展日用品厂 |\n| 蓬松发片夹 | ¥2-4 | 义乌浩福饰品 |\n| 洗脸发带（运动款） | ¥1.99 | 义乌薇杭饰品 |\n\n**套装拿货成本：¥5.5-8**，组3件→定价99K₫\n**毛利估算：~70-76%** ✅\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 问题\n\n1688 MCP 搜不到真正的套装产品链接（搜索算法偏向返回爆款单品）。以上数据是结合我之前搜到的单品价格整理的。\n\n**你想让我怎么做？**\n\nA. 手动搜索1688找具体套装链接 → 确认成本后入库\nB. 直接用以上候选品按你的成本公式跑利润核算 → 达到35%就入库\nC. 告诉我你现有Combo的**产品品类组合**，我帮你找1688对应货源"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2676,"output":1038,"cacheRead":126528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130242,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778852272685,"responseId":"065654b21d1e4f3fe0e1657c13df5a59"}}
