{"type":"message","id":"d42648dd","parentId":"7e61b644","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:54:39.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the data is there. But the user said the Feishu table is messy and no data was written. I think the issue is:\n\n1. I never actually wrote data to the Feishu table - I just collected data and showed analysis to the user but never actually used the feishu tools to write anything.2. The user shared a Feishu base URL (`https://my.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`) but this is a \"base\" (bitable) not a docx. The feishu_doc tool works with docx documents, not bitables directly.\n\n\nI need to be honest with the user - I never actually wrote anything to the Feishu table because I got stuck trying to figure out how to write to a bitable. The base URL they shared is a multi-dimensional table (base), not a docx, and my feishu_doc tool doesn't have the capability to write to bitables. I've been analyzing data and providing recommendations but haven't actually persisted anything to their Feishu table yet.\n\nI should ask them to either share a docx link instead so I can use feishu_doc, or give me more details about their bitable structure so I can find a different way to write the data there.\n\nBut honestly, looking back at the conversation, we spent most of our time collecting and analyzing data but never actually wrote anything to the table. I need to be straightforward about this - the user thinks the data has been written but it hasn't, and I should clarify that with them.\n\nThe real issue is that I can't write to a bitable (base), only to a docx document, so I need to explain this limitation and ask how they want to proceed.\n","thinkingSignature":"6e165a7461e7e5c8cccc815119762c0639a5032513a4ef980134aa490364d5d7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n坦白说——**飞书表格没有写入数据**。我之前一直没动，是因为：\n\n**你的链接是飞书 Base（多维表格）** `https://my.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`，但我的飞书工具（`feishu_doc`）**只能读写文档（Docx）**，不能直接操作 Base 多维表格。\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 解决方案\n\n**方案 1：用飞书文档写入（推荐）**\n把选品结果写入飞书文档 → 你再手动复制到 Base\n\n**方案 2：创建新的飞书文档作为选品报告**\n我直接创建一个新的飞书文档，把完整选品数据写进去（包含产品标题、TikTok售价、1688拿货价、利润核算、风险提示、入库建议）\n\n---\n\n**但首先我需要知道：**\n1. 你的飞书多维表格结构是什么样的？有哪些列（字段）？\n2. 或者你有一个飞书文档链接可以让我直接写？\n\n**我之前整理的选品数据都还在，告诉我怎么给你：**\n- A. 创建飞书文档 → 写入完整选品报告（你再复制到Base）\n- B. 直接在这里输出结构化表格 → 你手动录入\n- C. 你给我一个可以写入的飞书文档链接\n\n哪个方式方便？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":658,"cacheRead":152384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153288,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778853254439,"responseId":"06565886982773e18e8333983c6e4228"}}
