{"type":"message","id":"b1a0d7c3","parentId":"972ad2c9","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:58:02.541Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I now have the bitable structure! The table has 18 fields:\n1. 文本 (Text) - primary field\n2. 单选 (SingleSelect) - 选择\n3. 日期 (DateTime) - 日期\n4. 附件 (Attachment)\n5. 商品名称 (Text)\n6. 售价本地货币 (Number)\n7. 增长率 (Number)\n8. 月销量 (Number)\n9. 利润率 (%) (Number)\n10. 1688同款链接 (Url)\n11. 三级类目 (SingleSelect) - 发夹/发圈/抓夹/头饰/发簪/Hair Clips & Hair Pins/Hair Clips\n\n\n12. 1688价格CNY (Number)\n13. 站点 (SingleSelect) - 泰国/越南/VN\n14. 预计利润 (Number)\n15. 推荐等级 (SingleSelect) - A级/S级/S/A/B/C/D\n16. 采集状态 (SingleSelect) - 待审核/已采集\n17. IP风险 (SingleSelect) - 无/待确认\n18. 行动建议 (SingleSelect) - 正常采购首选30-50件/立即采购首选50-100件\n\nThe table contains 80 records total. I need to populate the key fields: 商品名称, 售价本地货币, 月销量, 增长率, 三级类目, 站点, and several calculated metrics including 预计利润, 利润率(%), 1688价格CNY, 推荐等级, and 采集状态.\n\nIP风险 should be marked as 无, 行动建议 depends on the recommendation level, and 1688同款链接 needs to be added for each product. Now I'm selecting the top products based on data from 908552 and 908424 with prices above 60K VND, focusing on those showing positive or stable growth metrics. There's also the COMBO 5 Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá from SÂU HOUSE at 69999₫ with monthly sales of 5333 units, though it's declining at -14.3% with 4.6 stars. For the hair accessories category, there's a spring hair tie set from Thiên Nhiên Ý at 59000₫ that moves 4888 units monthly with minimal decline. I'm seeing that Lò xo cột tóc thailann could work as a combo product despite the single decline rate, and Set 50 kẹp tóc shows strong growth at 88% but is priced at 36K. Since the user wants 60K+, I should prioritize the COMBO products and price points above 59K as starting candidates. 泰国站的数据是59K，勉强踩线。现在我需要整理这批产品并开始写入表格，先用curl测试一下写入功能是否正常。\n","thinkingSignature":"2f498b9be41efcab80d91447c70947edf583a5d96bac77e5cc52571a09e50d23"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！