{"type":"message","id":"f2f48818","parentId":"3f9ed864","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:00:15.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - \"文本\" works but \"商品名称\" and \"售价本地货币\" don't. The issue might be that the field names need to be exact as displayed, but the issue is with non-ASCII characters or maybe the field name format.\n\nLet me try with \"商品名称\" only, without the 售价本地货币.\n","thinkingSignature":"9f59ec36120361ca59d22050238c380d00e713ccd52fcbdeb3e9ea8d32852a9c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vecls5efmprb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"APP_ID=\"cli_a930f78f51399bc6\"\nAPP_SECRET=$(cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d['channels']['feishu']['accounts']['tts']['appSecret'])\")\n\nTOKEN=$(curl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\" | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n# Try 商品名称 alone\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tables/tblHU2do30jzinJT/records\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8\" \\\n  --data-raw '{\n    \"fields\": {\n      \"文本\": \"2026-05-15 测试-仅商品名\",\n      \"商品名称\": \"Lò xo cột tóc thailann phồng tóc\"\n    }\n  }' | python3 -m json.tool 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100486,"output":394,"cacheRead":1024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778853593461,"responseId":"065659da6c9d459b09fea1330c317e60"}}
