{"type":"message","id":"84361fd9","parentId":"790ddc78","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:02:17.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It works! The single select fields work too. Now let me test with all the fields I need to write, then batch write the data.\n\nLet me now write the actual product data. I need to:\n1. Get the product candidates we identified\n2. Calculate profits\n3. Batch write to the bitable\n\nLet me now write the real data. The candidates we found from the three categories:\n\nFrom 发夹类 (node 908552):\n1. [COMBO 5] Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá - 69,999₫, 月销5,333, -14.3%\n2. Set 50 Kẹp Tóc NOVSET - 86,300₫, 月销3,221, -29.2%\n3. Lò xo cột tóc thailann - 59,000₫, 月销4,888, -14.3%\n\n\n4. Kẹp tóc nơ bông (丝绒蝴蝶结发夹) - 35,000₫, 月销8,000, 持平\n5. Băng đô floral (花朵发带) - 34,780₫, 月销4,000, +0.6%\n6. Kẹp xược độn phồng tóc (蓬松发片夹) - 22,500₫, 月销3,000, +22.9%\n\nWait, the user wanted 60K+ products. Let me re-read what we found.\n\nLooking back at the data, the best performing 60K+ items are [COMBO 5] Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá at 69,999₫ with 5,333 monthly sales, and Set 50 Kẹp Tóc NOVSET at 86,300₫ with 3,221 monthly sales. The category data shows Vietnamese customers respond well to tiered gift combos and children's accessories at this price point, so I should focus the final selection on these higher-priced bundles rather than the lower-priced singles.\n\nNow I need to verify the profit margins using the user's cost structure—with the platform taking 39.5% in fees, I have roughly 84,729₫ to work with per item, which gives me enough room to calculate realistic profitability for each candidate. Now I'm working through the profit calculation for the Combo 4 Món at 140,050₫. With platform and creator fees totaling 55,321₫, that leaves 84,729₫ for product cost, logistics, and ad spend. If logistics runs about 8,000₫ and I reserve 10,000₫ for ads, I'm left with roughly 66,729₫ for the actual product cost—which translates to about ¥19, giving us a comfortable 38-42% margin depending on the exact product cost. This confirms the pricing strategy works for the user's higher-priced combo products. The 1688 tool doesn't have a straightforward way to find multi-item combo products, so I should work with what I've identified and calculate profits for the top candidates. I can write the product data directly to the Feishu table since I've confirmed I have access—it looks like the existing records are mostly empty templates, so I'll populate them with the candidates I've found. Now I'm identifying the best-performing products from the TikTok data—particularly those with strong sales velocity and growth metrics—to write into the Feishu sheet for the user. Writing product data...\n","thinkingSignature":"b0fd67797520f48b6c0717561c1efd254a1727827e80fcc1fc6d6ee07c95e3dc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8e8l2shkj3qa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"APP_ID=\"cli_a930f78f51399bc6\"\nAPP_SECRET=$(cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d['channels']['feishu']['accounts']['tts']['appSecret'])\")\n\nTOKEN=$(curl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\" | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n# Test URL field and multiple fields together\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tables/tblHU2do30jzinJT/records\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8\" \\\n  --data-raw '{\n    \"fields\": {\n      \"文本\": \"2026-05-15 测试-完整字段\",\n      \"商品名称\": \"Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá Combo 5 Món\",\n      \"售价本地货币\": 69999,\n      \"月销量\": 5333,\n      \"增长率\": -14.3,\n      \"1688价格CNY\": 8.5,\n      \"预计利润\": 22.5,\n      \"利润率(%)\": 32.1,\n      \"三级类目\": \"发夹\",\n      \"站点\": \"VN\",\n      \"推荐等级\": \"B\",\n      \"采集状态\": \"已采集\",\n      \"IP风险\": \"无\",\n      \"行动建议\": \"正常采购首选30-50件\"\n    }\n  }' | python3 -m json.tool 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":585,"output":1195,"cacheRead":103168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104948,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778853713681,"responseId":"06565a5299c6ba57b53e437d3ddceb5b"}}
