{"type":"message","id":"e9e4e407","parentId":"a2067665","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:03:33.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is likely that when I use `-d '...'` with single quotes containing non-ASCII characters, the shell might not be preserving the encoding correctly. But actually even with the ASCII-only `1688链接` field, it still fails. The error says `FieldNameNotFound` for `1688链接`.\n\nWait - `1688链接` - this field name contains ASCII characters (\"1688\" and \"链接\"). The field name in the bitable is `1688同款链接` (which I had mapped to `1688同款链接`). But `1688链接` might not exist. \n\nLet me re-check the actual field names from the API response:\n1. 文本 (Text)\n2. 单选 (SingleSelect)\n\n\n3. 日期 (DateTime)\n4. 附件 (Attachment)\n5. 商品名称 (Text) ✅ works\n6. 售价本地货币 (Number with formatter \"0.0\")\n7. 增长率 (Number with formatter \"0.0\")\n8. 月销量 (Number with formatter \"0.0\")\n9. 利润率(%) (Number with formatter \"0.0\")\n10. 1688同款链接 (URL) ❌ - I tried `1688链接` which doesn't exist!\n11. 三级类目 (SingleSelect)\n12. 1688价格CNY (Number)\n13. 站点 (SingleSelect)\n\nI see the problem now - I was using the wrong field name. The actual field is `1688同款链接`, not `1688链接`.\n\nLooking at the test results, I've confirmed that `文本`, `商品名称`, `月销量`, `三级类目`, `站点` all work, but I'm still trying to figure out why `售价本地货币` and `增长率` are failing - it might be a formatter issue or something else entirely.\n\nThe error message specifically says the field name can't be found, which is odd since the field list shows it should exist. I'm wondering if the API is having trouble with fields that have number formatters, or if there's something else going on. Let me test the remaining fields to see which ones actually work and which ones don't.\n","thinkingSignature":"9189e2d8a51e0e07197833e1a0ea6a91fcdb140b0761a4843a2c5250e2bde675"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5uwi29c77wd1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"APP_ID=\"cli_a930f78f51399bc6\"\nAPP_SECRET=$(cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d['channels']['feishu']['accounts']['tts']['appSecret'])\")\n\nTOKEN=$(curl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\" | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n# Test number fields one by one\necho \"=== Test 增长率 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tables/tblHU2do30jzinJT/records\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8\" \\\n  -d '{\"fields\":{\"文本\":\"2026-05-15\",\"商品名称\":\"Test Growth\",\"增长率\":-14.3}}' | python3 -m json.tool\n\necho \"=== Test 1688价格CNY ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tables/tblHU2do30jzinJT/records\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8\" \\\n  -d '{\"fields\":{\"文本\":\"2026-05-15\",\"商品名称\":\"Test 1688 Price\",\"1688价格CNY\":2.5}}' | python3 -m json.tool\n\necho \"=== Test 预计利润 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tables/tblHU2do30jzinJT/records\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8\" \\\n  -d '{\"fields\":{\"文本\":\"2026-05-15\",\"商品名称\":\"Test Profit\",\"预计利润\":16.8}}' | python3 -m json.tool\n\necho \"=== Test 利润率(%) ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tables/tblHU2do30jzinJT/records\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8\" \\\n  -d '{\"fields\":{\"文本\":\"2026-05-15\",\"商品名称\":\"Test Margin\",\"利润率\":28.5}}' | python3 -m json.tool"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":545,"output":1145,"cacheRead":104896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778853782908,"responseId":"06565a98ee1a2ed6279d8302b4065ad0"}}
