{"type":"message","id":"dc036602","parentId":"947a5c7b","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:07:01.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the pattern. Some fields work and some don't. Specifically:- ✅ Text fields: 文本, 商品名称\n- ✅ Single-select: 三级类目, 站点, 推荐等级, 采集状态, IP风险, 行动建议- ✅ Number fields (without formatter): 月销量, 增长率\n- ❌ Number fields with formatter: 售价本地货币, 1688价格CNY, 预计利润, 利润率\n- ❌ URL field: 1688链接When I put all fields together, the failure is probably because of the formatter-related fields. Let me test just the problematic fields to confirm.Also, I noticed something interesting - when I tested 月销量 and 增长率 they worked. But 售价本地货币, 1688价格CNY, 预计利润, 利润率 don't work. The difference is that 月销量 and 增长率 don't have formatters, while the others do.\n\nLooking at the field list from the API:\n\n\n- 售价本地货币 has a formatter set to \"0.0\"\n- 1688价格CNY also has a formatter of \"0.0\"\n- 预计利润 has a formatter of \"0.0\"\n- 利润率 has a formatter of \"0.0\"\n\nBut 月销量 doesn't have a formatter at all, which is why it worked. This might mean the API requires a specific format for fields that have custom formatters, or maybe they're read-only somehow.\n\nI also noticed that 1688链接 uses the URL type (15), which might need special handling. Let me try sending these fields with the proper number formatting and see if that resolves the issue.\n","thinkingSignature":"a2bfea93aeaab469dffb3b7d314722459765bb9fa516371b447312661050021e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4x3p5vzjet8i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /tmp/test_feishu4.py 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":958,"output":372,"cacheRead":110528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778854009535,"responseId":"06565b7a78e1acbd576a4a8a3fa948ec"}}
