{"type":"message","id":"1b22d3e0","parentId":"4f04fd73","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:09:57.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 6 products were written successfully to the Feishu bitable. Now let me report back to the user that the data has been written, and summarize what was done.\n","thinkingSignature":"a6b4743a7a1e02a78cc57d29c41d639ecef329e224781b4f9e897ecea12a086e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**✅ 已写入飞书表格！** 6条选品数据全部成功入库。\n\n---\n\n## 📊 写入产品清单\n\n| # | 产品名称 | 售价 | 月销量 | 增长率 | 预估利润 | 利润率 | 推荐等级 |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | Lò xo cột tóc thailann Chun Hoa Voi（发圈） | 59,000₫ | 4,888 | -14.3% | 17.5% | 29.6% | A |\n| 2 | [COMBO 5 KẸP 5 MÀU] Kẹp Càng Cua Voan Đính Đá | 69,999₫ | 5,333 | -14.3% | 20.2% | 28.9% | A |\n| 3 | Set 50 Kẹp Tóc Dễ Thương NOVSET（儿童发夹套装） | 86,300₫ | 3,221 | -29.2% | 24.8% | 28.7% | B |\n| 4 | Sét 10 Chun Thái Lò Xo（发圈套装）📈 | 49,000₫ | 2,978 | **+20.8%** | 15.2% | 31.0% | A |\n| 5 | Kẹp xược độn phồng tóc（蓬松发片夹）🆕 | 22,500₫ | 4,500 | **+22.9%** | 8.5% | 37.8% | **S** |\n| 6 | Miếng dán tóc mái（刘海贴片）🆕 | 14,999₫ | 8,095 | **+5.0%** | 5.8% | **38.7%** | **S** |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 注意事项\n\n**预估利润和利润率是我根据你给的费率结构（平台佣金13% + 交易手续费3.5% + 增值税12% + 提现1% + 达人佣金10% = 合计39.5%）+ 假设的国际物流费估算的，不是精准值。** 实际成本需要你拿具体1688链接核价后重新计算。\n\n另外，**1688同款链接**这个字段的URL格式要求比较严格（必须写成 `{\"link\": \"https://...\", \"text\": \"...\"}` 格式），我暂时写的是占位链接，你需要手动替换成真实1688产品链接。\n\n**现在去飞书表格确认一下数据是否正常？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":369,"output":618,"cacheRead":116736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117723,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778854176094,"responseId":"06565c207e2cd2bd7d12f7ab212b5879"}}
